msgstr "آرڈر تبدیل کریں: %(code)s"

#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/order/change.html:18
#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/order/change_contact.html:12
#: control/templates/pretixcontrol/order/change_locale.html:12
